{"tid":1624660,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［和理非Twitter大行動］易過借火既Twitter戰線！！！","createTime":"2019-10-05T04:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T08:46:15.000Z","uid":39021,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b3e78a6c0df6cc10bf6672889b34456a689f5221","tid":1624660,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:30:41.000Z","msg":"轉至美國戰線post<br />\n<blockquote>-華府嘅官好多時只用 twitter<br />\n-幫手瘋狂 Twitter 香港情況，但最好唔好提示威者暴力同拉返同五大訴求有關</blockquote><br />\n即係我地要幫手擴大Twitter戰線！！！<br />\n唔出post都唔緊要，淨係like同retweet都非常足夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 首先去註冊個Twitter account，係要電話號碼做認證，但你唔需要公開電話號碼<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>一定一定一定要Follow既係gphone，周庭同埋Solomon Yue</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoshuawongcf&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqsg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=b52c8a47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/chowtingagnes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchowtingagnes&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqsg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=8d8fe137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/chowtingagnes</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqsg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=89d21ac6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SolomonYue</a><br />\n點解？因為佢地會like同retweet有利外國戰線既post，只要跟住佢地like retweet就可以啦！！<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>唔建議公式化地跟隨指示like post，因為會好容易比Twitter suspend！</strong></span><br />\n建議大家只需要睇下自己Twitter個Home，睇下gphone佢地retweet咗乜野<br />\n有咩post值得like就like，當係facebook咁自然地玩<br />\n<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>見到有值得follow既人就follow，慢慢擴大你既個人戰線</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下既人都可以follow<br />\n美國CIA記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HongKongHermit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHongKongHermit&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqsg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=6b12d0f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HongKongHermit</a><br />\nRubio：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcorubio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqsg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=5c80bc79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/marcorubio</a><br />\nPelosi：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SpeakerPelosi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSpeakerPelosi&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqsg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=f719fad6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SpeakerPelosi</a><br />\n好幫香港人既丹麥議員：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/uffeelbaek\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fuffeelbaek&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqsg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=4eadd3a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/uffeelbaek</a><br />\n駐香港記者Scotford：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RichScotford\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRichScotford&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqsg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=8aba1627\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/RichScotford</a><br />\n美國國會及行政當局中國委員會：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/CECCgov\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCECCgov&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqsg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=201ccdb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/CECCgov</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每日堅持上Twitter，步步擴大戰線</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"777c6ab9f239d491f002c28a40732bf19ed1fba0","tid":1624660,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:31:35.000Z","msg":"大家可以分享下有咩人值得follow<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65724d116a68a3f72dafb220a4989ca7594e4830","tid":1624660,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:32:57.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"4f636696d9604eff0e081065fa1cb9326e93f904","tid":1624660,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:34:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3282a9be98d66683fc0f8486a8e00353a29f6d3b","tid":1624660,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:35:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4682bbaf6b737241bdb0c00a7c533e88e16934d3","tid":1624660,"uid":178933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:37:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kHsnS8G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkHsnS8G.jpg&h=c4313895&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/btXvhAm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbtXvhAm.jpg&h=2e97bba6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ec74e9fa927d487331eabe1bcff86d807db1db6","tid":1624660,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img s